            <li>• Creation of design artifacts such as journey maps, wireframes, prototypes</li>
            <li>• Familiarity with design, research, and collaboration tools such as Figma, Adobe Suite, Sketch, Miro, Tableau or similar platforms</li>
            <li>• Ability to produce clear research documentation and communicate insights to technical and non-technical audiences</li>
            <li>• Understanding of agile software development and working within cross-functional teams</li>
